<h2 class="bold font-l">Super Smash Bros Brawl - Meta Knight is Broken</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Meta Knight is shown to be considered the most powerful character in Brawl, if not the most powerful in Smash history. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GameBreaker" class='trope-example-link'>Game-Breaker</a></p>
